{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "story_rfrost_set_1", "eventName": "尋鄉", "entryType": "NONE", "storyCode": null, "avgTag": "幕間", "storyName": "尋鄉", "storyInfo": "FROST與一位薩卡茲老獵人結伴，在薩米的無盡冰原中尋找各自的回家路。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“Elias，別來無恙。”"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“聽說你去了南方，或許現在，我們正身處這片大陸的兩極。”"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“薩米是個寧靜祥和的地方。我很喜歡這裡的環境和氣候，它們偶爾會讓我想起老家。”"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“有趣的是，我很期待ASH得知我們將她列出危險地區的地圖當作旅遊指南後的反應。”"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“我們的目標是一致的，這場穿越一定事出有因，而我一定要找出它的答案。”"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“古怪問題的答案總是藏在古怪的地方，或許我們中的一個就能找到它。”"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“祝你好運。”"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_iceforest_1", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_458_rfrost_1#1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "FROST"}, "figure_art": "char_458_rfrost_1#1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "獵人在屏息等待，手指搭上了板機。"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "視野裡有一隻羽獸，正在林中來回逡巡，在雪地上留下片片腳印。"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它同樣是一位覓食者，在這片嚴酷的環境中尋找可以讓自己的生命延續下去的其他生命。"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它彷彿看到了什麼，挺起了修長的脖頸，鋒利的喙瞄準了獵物的方向。"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在同一瞬間，羽獸張開雙翼，獵人扣下了板機。"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_arrowshot", "channel": "1"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_wing", "channel": "2"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_053", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "char_458_rfrost_1#1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "char_458_rfrost_1#1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就差一點！", "name": "FROST"}, "figure_art": "char_458_rfrost_1#1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_053", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "的確只差一點。", "name": "年邁的薩卡茲獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "char_458_rfrost_1#1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "運氣真壞。", "name": "FROST"}, "figure_art": "char_458_rfrost_1#1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_053", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有的羽獸善於捕捉空氣的流動，有的擁有格外敏感的腳爪，可以感受到大地最輕微的震動。", "name": "年邁的薩卡茲獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對於不同的獵物，有不同的隱藏身形的手段。", "name": "年邁的薩卡茲獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "char_458_rfrost_1#1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好吧，又學到了一課。這樣看來也不能說是運氣不好——我剛才弄丟的那隻屬於哪一種？", "name": "FROST"}, "figure_art": "char_458_rfrost_1#1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_053", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "都不是，只是它尚命不該絕。", "name": "年邁的薩卡茲獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "char_458_rfrost_1#1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這也是寫在預言裡的？", "name": "FROST"}, "figure_art": "char_458_rfrost_1#1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_053", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你依然不相信。", "name": "年邁的薩卡茲獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "char_458_rfrost_1#1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我只是，無法理解。", "name": "FROST"}, "figure_art": "char_458_rfrost_1#1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在我們認識的這段時間裡，您一直是一個聰明的獵人。經驗豐富，而且敏銳。", "name": "FROST"}, "figure_art": "char_458_rfrost_1#1"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "何況，您看起來依然健康，我實在不能相信您說的……", "name": "FROST"}, "figure_art": "char_458_rfrost_1#1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_053", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "經驗並不足取，判斷也不重要。此刻你正身處於這趟旅程，這已經足夠。", "name": "年邁的薩卡茲獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "char_458_rfrost_1#1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“在這片土地上，有特殊的生存法則”？", "name": "FROST"}, "figure_art": "char_458_rfrost_1#1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_053", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "正是如此。", "name": "年邁的薩卡茲獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在，我們應該繼續向北出發了。", "name": "年邁的薩卡茲獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "char_458_rfrost_1#1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果已知的情報沒錯的話，森林的北方，只有荒涼的冰原。越往北走，可供捕獲的獵物就越少。", "name": "FROST"}, "figure_art": "char_458_rfrost_1#1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們剛錯過的，可能就是我們最後一頓食物。", "name": "FROST"}, "figure_art": "char_458_rfrost_1#1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_053", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不必為此擔心，預言只提到了我自己的死亡，而你，一定會找到你一直在尋找的東西。", "name": "年邁的薩卡茲獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.8, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_snowconutryinside", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "數日前"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_053", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "char_458_rfrost_1#1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以生命停止為終點的旅行？", "name": "FROST"}, "figure_art": "char_458_rfrost_1#1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_053", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我看見了，我已經在預言中看到了我的死亡。但是在那之前，我有一個請求。", "name": "年邁的薩卡茲獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請帶我向北走吧，就從這裡出發，一直向北走去，直到走出這片樹林。如果到那時我還沒有嚥氣，就請繼續向北走吧。", "name": "年邁的薩卡茲獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我已經在這間木屋裡度過了足夠漫長的安穩歲月，在死之前，我還想看一看從未見過的景色。", "name": "年邁的薩卡茲獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我已年老力衰，這是我無法獨自完成的旅行。所以，我要請求你的幫助。", "name": "年邁的薩卡茲獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "char_458_rfrost_1#1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老先生，如果這真的是您的臨終心願，我當然會竭盡全力幫您實現。", "name": "FROST"}, "figure_art": "char_458_rfrost_1#1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我不能理解，為何您會認定自己大限將至？我甚至不能確定，“一直向北走去”，這能否算是一個心願……", "name": "FROST"}, "figure_art": "char_458_rfrost_1#1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_053", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真有趣，即使在薩米，也不會有人稱一個薩卡茲為“先生”。", "name": "年邁的薩卡茲獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "char_458_rfrost_1#1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我很尊敬您。", "name": "FROST"}, "figure_art": "char_458_rfrost_1#1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_053", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "預言已然明確，最終我們一定會到達那個地方。", "name": "年邁的薩卡茲獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是我最後的請求。請帶我走吧，就像預言中所展示的那樣。", "name": "年邁的薩卡茲獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不會讓你白白幫我這個忙的，在旅程的終點，會有我提供的報酬。你也會找到你一直在尋找的。", "name": "年邁的薩卡茲獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只有一個月亮的地方。", "name": "年邁的薩卡茲獵人"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "amount": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_iceforest_1", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "channel": "2"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_053", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "char_458_rfrost_1#1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "char_458_rfrost_1#1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "按指南針顯示的，我們的確在向北前進。但是氣候和周圍分布的植物，卻絲毫沒有表現出更明顯的寒帶特徵。", "name": "FROST"}, "figure_art": "char_458_rfrost_1#1"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "指南針和常識，一定有一個出了錯。", "name": "FROST"}, "figure_art": "char_458_rfrost_1#1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_053", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "薩米之所以容得下一個薩卡茲在這裡養老，是因為這裡有許多比魔族更麻煩的東西。", "name": "年邁的薩卡茲獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "繼續向前走吧，我們沒有偏離方向。", "name": "年邁的薩卡茲獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "char_458_rfrost_1#1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您為何會這麼肯定？按您所說，您之前從來沒有走到過這裡，對這裡也並不熟悉。", "name": "FROST"}, "figure_art": "char_458_rfrost_1#1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_053", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，我從未踏足過這片森林。", "name": "年邁的薩卡茲獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我們並不依賴經驗認識現實。當你發現經驗並不能讓你看清現實的時候，你就離觸及現實更近了一點。", "name": "年邁的薩卡茲獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "char_458_rfrost_1#1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好吧，這聽起來倒很像是經驗之談。", "name": "FROST"}, "figure_art": "char_458_rfrost_1#1"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無論如何，我得承認這個世界有太多超出我常識的部分……所以，我們還要繼續向前？", "name": "FROST"}, "figure_art": "char_458_rfrost_1#1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_053", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒錯——咳，咳咳……我們要繼續向前。", "name": "年邁的薩卡茲獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "char_458_rfrost_1#1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許，我們也可以先休息一下。", "name": "FROST"}, "figure_art": "char_458_rfrost_1#1"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_053", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不錯的提議，我們還有時間，我也還有時間。", "name": "年邁的薩卡茲獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "FROST在樹旁清掃了一小片積雪，在上面鋪了一層落葉，讓老獵人坐下。"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_053", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "char_458_rfrost_1#1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝。", "name": "年邁的薩卡茲獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "char_458_rfrost_1#1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是第九天了。", "name": "FROST"}, "figure_art": "char_458_rfrost_1#1"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "獵物的確在逐漸變少，物資同樣很緊張——還要考慮到返程的路。", "name": "FROST"}, "figure_art": "char_458_rfrost_1#1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_053", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不用在意我，在到達旅程的終點之後，將會是你獨自的歸途。", "name": "年邁的薩卡茲獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "char_458_rfrost_1#1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，我還是有一些疑問。", "name": "FROST"}, "figure_art": "char_458_rfrost_1#1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您是如此地篤信這個預言，那麼預言是否給出了一些具體的訊息？", "name": "FROST"}, "figure_art": "char_458_rfrost_1#1"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "例如這趟旅行的終點，以及，我們該做怎樣的準備。", "name": "FROST"}, "figure_art": "char_458_rfrost_1#1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "甚至是更根本的問題，到底是預言指示您應當去某個地方，還是說，這趟旅程只是一個願望……我有些不明白了。", "name": "FROST"}, "figure_art": "char_458_rfrost_1#1"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_053", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的困惑可以理解。多數人提出問題，只會在得到實際的答案之後才能行動。", "name": "年邁的薩卡茲獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是預言從不給予答案，這並非預言運作的方式。", "name": "年邁的薩卡茲獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "char_458_rfrost_1#1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是卻說明了您的死亡？", "name": "FROST"}, "figure_art": "char_458_rfrost_1#1"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_053", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "死亡也並非答案。", "name": "年邁的薩卡茲獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "char_458_rfrost_1#1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在認識您之前，我也聽這裡的人們提到過，“預言”。難道在這裡，這是一種常見的技能？", "name": "FROST"}, "figure_art": "char_458_rfrost_1#1"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_053", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其實我們每個人都會預言。我們看到堆積的烏雲，便知道即將要下雨。就是這樣簡單。", "name": "年邁的薩卡茲獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "char_458_rfrost_1#1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這依然很難理解。", "name": "FROST"}, "figure_art": "char_458_rfrost_1#1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_053", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼，我們可以不談論預言，只談論旅行。", "name": "年邁的薩卡茲獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "char_458_rfrost_1#1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，不僅是這一次，您和我說起過許多以前的旅程。如果您還記得的話。", "name": "FROST"}, "figure_art": "char_458_rfrost_1#1"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "會下雨的高塔，海面下的湖泊，埋在地底的裂谷，巨獸脊背上的城市，還有，“不存在的故鄉”。", "name": "FROST"}, "figure_art": "char_458_rfrost_1#1"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "故事的開頭都很吸引人，但是您從來沒有講完過。", "name": "FROST"}, "figure_art": "char_458_rfrost_1#1"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_053", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我當然記得，不管是這些旅行還是故事。", "name": "年邁的薩卡茲獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "旅行應當在還值得回味的時候結束，故事也應當在聽眾尚有興趣的時候結束。", "name": "年邁的薩卡茲獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "char_458_rfrost_1#1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喔喔，這可不能當作打發聽眾的藉口。", "name": "FROST"}, "figure_art": "char_458_rfrost_1#1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_053", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼就當作打發時間，讓我把最後的故事講完吧。", "name": "年邁的薩卡茲獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請提醒我一下，之前講到哪裡了？不，不用，我想起來了。", "name": "年邁的薩卡茲獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$drift_intro", "key": "$drift_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最終，我陪著那頭被詛咒的惡獸找到了那位術師。惡獸憤怒地質問道：“我的故鄉到底在哪裡？”", "name": "年邁的薩卡茲獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“萬事萬物都有起源，既然有起源，就一定有誕生的地方。為什麼我卻沒有？難道我原本就不該存在？”", "name": "年邁的薩卡茲獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "術師答道：“這就是詛咒的規則。你用故鄉換來了智慧，還有令所有人畏懼的力量，但是你永遠地失去了故鄉，你的確不該存在！”", "name": "年邁的薩卡茲獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "惡獸非常憤怒，想要咬死術師。但它還是冷靜了下來。", "name": "年邁的薩卡茲獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "報仇是無濟於事的，這樣也無法解決它自身存在的矛盾。而不合理的存在，注定是要消失的。", "name": "年邁的薩卡茲獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最終，被詛咒的惡獸選擇不停地奔跑。只要它永遠不停留在任何一個地方，這片大地對它而言就沒有“故鄉”和“他鄉”的區別。", "name": "年邁的薩卡茲獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "多麼智慧的惡獸，用這種方式解決了自己的存在危機。但是，我沒有力氣陪伴它繼續奔跑了，只能選擇留在那棟小木屋裡安度餘生。", "name": "年邁的薩卡茲獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "char_458_rfrost_1#1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "充滿隱喻的故事。", "name": "FROST"}, "figure_art": "char_458_rfrost_1#1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_053", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "人們透過隱喻來認識現實。", "name": "年邁的薩卡茲獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "char_458_rfrost_1#1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "並非透過經驗認識現實，而是藉由隱喻來認識現實。", "name": "FROST"}, "figure_art": "char_458_rfrost_1#1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_053", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你逐漸明白了。", "name": "年邁的薩卡茲獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "char_458_rfrost_1#1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，這次預言之旅的終點，也和“故鄉”有關？", "name": "FROST"}, "figure_art": "char_458_rfrost_1#1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_053", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這正是我所期待的。", "name": "年邁的薩卡茲獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "char_458_rfrost_1#1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我依舊很好奇，在您來到薩米安居之前，究竟去過多少地方？", "name": "FROST"}, "figure_art": "char_458_rfrost_1#1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_053", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "足夠多，多到我的生命在任何時候終結都不能算是一件憾事。", "name": "年邁的薩卡茲獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有時是作為傭兵，有時是作為獵人，更多時候是單純的旅行者。", "name": "年邁的薩卡茲獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "char_458_rfrost_1#1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在熱愛冒險這一點上，我們的確有共同之處。", "name": "FROST"}, "figure_art": "char_458_rfrost_1#1"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_053", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“未曾見過的風景是無價之寶。”", "name": "年邁的薩卡茲獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "char_458_rfrost_1#1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為了欣賞值得觀看的東西，我們總要遠行。", "name": "FROST"}, "figure_art": "char_458_rfrost_1#1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_053", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就像那隻永遠不會停下的惡獸。", "name": "年邁的薩卡茲獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "char_458_rfrost_1#1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "另一層隱喻。", "name": "FROST"}, "figure_art": "char_458_rfrost_1#1"}, {"id": 225, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_053", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼，該你了。", "name": "年邁的薩卡茲獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "同為旅行者，你也一定有許多值得分享的故事。", "name": "年邁的薩卡茲獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "char_458_rfrost_1#1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的確有許多旅行的故事可以講述，但恐怕那對您來說同樣難以理解。", "name": "FROST"}, "figure_art": "char_458_rfrost_1#1"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_053", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你來自很遙遠的地方。", "name": "年邁的薩卡茲獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "char_458_rfrost_1#1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "的確很遙遠，甚至遠遠超出了我們的認知。", "name": "FROST"}, "figure_art": "char_458_rfrost_1#1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_053", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼，應該說，是很久遠的地方？", "name": "年邁的薩卡茲獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "char_458_rfrost_1#1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……這是個很難回答的問題。", "name": "FROST"}, "figure_art": "char_458_rfrost_1#1"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_053", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不必在意，我不會追問答案。欣賞故事，並不需要弄清每一個細節。", "name": "年邁的薩卡茲獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請繼續你的講述吧。", "name": "年邁的薩卡茲獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "char_458_rfrost_1#1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好吧，如果您願意聽的話。", "name": "FROST"}, "figure_art": "char_458_rfrost_1#1"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個故事我幾乎沒有對其他人講過，但為了讓您理解我所來自的地方，這卻是個很好的例子。", "name": "FROST"}, "figure_art": "char_458_rfrost_1#1"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那並不是一次值得誇耀的冒險，故事需要從一次迫降開始說起。", "name": "FROST"}, "figure_art": "char_458_rfrost_1#1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“未知的旅程永遠是令人欣喜的，儘管常常伴隨著風險。但你明白的，我永遠無法拒絕。”"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“人在旅程中總會有些收穫，有時是令人欣喜的景色，有時是另一種看待世界的眼光。”"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“如那個智慧的老獵人所說，我們無法容忍沒有答案的問題存在。就彷彿每一把鎖，都有與之配套生產的鑰匙。”"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“但這只是我們一廂情願的理解，並不是自然造物的邏輯。有點像東方的禪語，不是嗎？”"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“我正在嘗試去理解，這或許對我們真正解決問題有所幫助。”"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們到了。", "name": "年邁的薩卡茲獵人"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_snow_2", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_053", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "char_458_rfrost_1#1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在森林的北面，是這樣的景象？", "name": "FROST"}, "figure_art": "char_458_rfrost_1#1"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_053", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡就是“故鄉”。", "name": "年邁的薩卡茲獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "char_458_rfrost_1#1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您是說這片廢墟？", "name": "FROST"}, "figure_art": "char_458_rfrost_1#1"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老獵人搖晃地坐了下來，長途跋涉的旅行已經耗光了他最後一絲精力。"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他望著前方的斷壁殘垣，神情就像在欣賞最美的風景。"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_053", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "char_458_rfrost_1#1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在這片廢墟上，曾經也有一座宏偉的城市。", "name": "年邁的薩卡茲獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它不只一次地被摧毀過，也不只一次地被重新建起。", "name": "年邁的薩卡茲獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "char_458_rfrost_1#1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這樣荒無人跡的地方，真的會有城市？", "name": "FROST"}, "figure_art": "char_458_rfrost_1#1"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_053", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "炮火下也曾有花海，焦土上也曾有高樓。", "name": "年邁的薩卡茲獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“卡茲戴爾”。", "name": "年邁的薩卡茲獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如預言所說，它終將成為所有薩卡茲的故鄉。", "name": "年邁的薩卡茲獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "char_458_rfrost_1#1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等，這不對——", "name": "FROST"}, "figure_art": "char_458_rfrost_1#1"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_battlefield", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_forest", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_iceforest_1", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_desert_1", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在一瞬間，周圍無數景色全部坍縮。"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "40_g2_glacier", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_458_rfrost_1#1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這究竟是……", "name": "FROST"}, "figure_art": "char_458_rfrost_1#1"}, {"id": 320, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "FROST環顧四周，眼前、身後，都只剩下無盡冰原。"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來時的路如日出時的露水般消失無痕，而手中的指南針的磁針紋絲不動，正指著前方。"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_458_rfrost_1#1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好消息是，我們可能沒有迷失方向。", "name": "FROST"}, "figure_art": "char_458_rfrost_1#1"}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果這也是您說的隱喻……老先生？", "name": "FROST"}, "figure_art": "char_458_rfrost_1#1"}, {"id": 327, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "FROST這才注意到，身邊的老人已經停止了呼吸。"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "年邁的獵人面朝空無一物的冰原，臉上滿是安詳。"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_458_rfrost_1#1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以生命停止為終點的旅行。", "name": "FROST"}, "figure_art": "char_458_rfrost_1#1"}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您最後的願望，應該算是完成了吧。", "name": "FROST"}, "figure_art": "char_458_rfrost_1#1"}, {"id": 334, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "FROST也在老獵人身邊坐了下來，兩個獵人一同欣賞著旅程終點的景色。"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "38_g21_skystarry_R1", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "天上，只有一個月亮。", "name": "FROST"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在日落相反的方向，天邊隱隱出現了一輪月亮。淡銀色的輪廓，和無盡冰原是一般顏色。"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "FROST後來才知道，在這片大地上，這是很少見的景象。"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“未曾見過的風景是無價之寶。”", "name": "FROST"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好吧，我願意接受這個報酬。", "name": "FROST"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}